text: Fraubrunnen is a municipality in the administrative district of Bern- Mittelland in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipalities of Büren zum Hof, Etzelkofen, Grafenried, Limpach, Mülchi, Schalunen and Zauggenried merged into the municipality of Fraubrunnen. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Bern-Mittelland
